text: Naomi Grace Scott (born 6 May 1993) is an English actress and singer. She is best known for starring as Princess Jasmine in Disney's musical fantasy movie Aladdin (2019). She also starred in Power Rangers (2017) and the action comedy movie Charlie's Angels (2019). ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English stage actors Category:English voice actors Category:Actors from London Category:Singers from London
